---
title: Marinated Bocconcini and Roasted Vegetable Salad with Croutons and Balsamic Dressing
description: Bocconcini pearls add richness and creaminess to a hearty salad packed full of arugula, baby spinach, tomatoes, peppers and mixed olives. Crunchy seasoned croutons and balsamic dressing add the perfect finishing touches.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/marinated-bocconcini-and-roasted-vegetable-salad-d14f7059.jpg
